---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Health Exercise Division | Taijutsu Health Class"
  description="Introducing the Seishinkai Health Exercise Division. Health exercise classes for middle-aged and older adults, including a Senior Karate Health Class and a Health Taijutsu class. Active in the Atsubetsu, Ooasa, and Kawashimo areas."
  lang="en"
  path="/en/dojo/kenko/"
>
  <section class="dojo-list">
    <div class="page-container">
      <div class="section__title-area">
        <span class="section-label">HEALTH CLASS</span>
        <h1 class="section-title">Seishinkai Health Exercises</h1>
      </div>

      <p class="detail-page__lead">
        [Seishinkai Senior Karate Health Class / Health Taijutsu]<br />
        The Seishinkai Health Division began its activities in 2010 (Heisei 22),
        based on the Muroki-style health exercises (<a
          href="https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/室木洋一"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener">devised by the late Sensei Yoichi Muroki</a
        >), incorporating cool-down exercise elements and breathing techniques
        from the taijutsu (karate kobudo) practiced at Seishinkai.<br />
        Afterward, we ran health exercise programs incorporating elements of
        seitai (bodywork) and various taijutsu techniques as one-off seminars,
        but we decided to hold regular classes with the aim of helping
        middle-aged and older adults lead healthy daily lives.<br />
        Excellent full-body exercise and cool-down movements improve
        circulation and boost physical strength (immunity).
      </p>

      <p class="detail-page__note">
        We are currently accepting advance registration for the Senior Karate
        Health Class and the Health Taijutsu Class.
      </p>

      <h2 class="detail-page__heading">★★For a Healthy Mind and Body★★</h2>
      <table class="table">
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <th>● Headquarters Class</th>
            <td>Senior Karate</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>○ Ooasa Class</th>
            <td>-</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p class="detail-page__note">
        ※Depending on circumstances, the day of the week and start time may
        change. A heating fee applies during the winter season.
      </p>

      <div class="detail-gallery">
        <figure>
          <img
            src="/assets/images/legacy/dojo/kenko/img3.jpg"
            alt="A health exercise class session"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </figure>
        <figure>
          <a
            href="mailto:muroki-taku@seishinryu.info?subject=Kobujutsu Health Exercise Class Registration"
          >
            <img
              src="/assets/images/legacy/images/muro.jpg"
              alt="Taku Muroki, Health Exercise Division Head"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </a>
          <figcaption>Taku Muroki, Health Exercise Division Head</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure>
          <a
            href="mailto:muroki-taku@seishinryu.info?subject=Kobujutsu Health Exercise Class Registration"
          >
            <img
              src="/assets/images/legacy/dojo/kenko/img4.jpg"
              alt="Health exercises that move the whole body without strain"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </a>
          <figcaption>Gentle full-body movement for everyone</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <h2 class="detail-page__heading">Health Exercise Division</h2>
      <p>
        ◆ Founded: August 2010 (Heisei 22)<br />
        ◆ Head: <a
          href="mailto:muroki-taku@seishinryu.info?subject=Kobujutsu Health Exercise Class Registration"
          >Taku Muroki</a
        >
      </p>

      <h2 class="detail-page__heading">Participation Fees</h2>
      <p>
        ■ Enrollment fee ¥7,000<br />
        ■ Annual fee ¥5,800 (includes insurance)<br />
        ■ Monthly fee ¥4,800–6,500 (paid via Japan Post Bank account debit)
      </p>

      <p>
        <a href="mailto:karate@seishinkan.ne.jp?subject=Health Taijutsu Class Inquiry"
          >Email Registration & Inquiries</a
        ><br />
        <a href="/assets/pdf/kenko2021.pdf" target="_blank"
          >Health Club Brochure (PDF)</a
        >
      </p>

      <p class="detail-page__back">
        <a href="/en/dojo/">← Back to the Dojo & Class List</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
